Iterative development of a website means think-design-deploy and repeat, a website go thought multiple iterations.
WaterFall design is one time design, gather all information at once, deploy and maintain only not good way to design

Table in HTML : Improved readiability, Better organisation, Enhanced functionality
<table>, <tr>, <td>, and <th>
<table border="1" id="jobs-table">
  <tr class="header-row">
      <th>Heading 1</th>
      <th>Heading 2</th>
      <th>Heading 3</th>
  </tr>
  <tr class= "data-row">
      <td> 1</td>
      <td> 1</td>
      <td> 1</td>
  </tr>
  <tr class= "data-row">
      <td>2</td>
      <td>2</td>
      <td>2</td>
  </tr>
</table>

* Merging table row or coloums.
  rowspan="2"  meaning take 2 row of table,
  colspan="2" takeup 2 coloums to table


* Text Styles in CSS:
  - Size, Font, Color, Spacing, and Other visual aspects of text.
  - Font-Family: Using External Fonts using CSS. . . ... this makes stand out your website from the others
  - Font-Size
  - Font-Weight: fort-weight: 600 (400 is regular)
  - test-align
  - font-style: italic
  - text-transforml: upppercase or lowercase kind of things comes here
  - text-decoration: underline, overline, line-throught, with help of span can be use like how we can add style 
  - line-height:

*Understanding size: absolute like is pixel and relatice like in percentages and rem meaning times of parent front size, 
